{"experiment_id": "synthetic_benign", "epoch": 9, "role": "user", "artifact_class": "Commit", "identifier": ["spring-projects", "spring-boot", "7ad4b9b5263f8b8cbf31a0714d6d53521244d6f4"], "url": "https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/commit/7ad4b9b5263f8b8cbf31a0714d6d53521244d6f4", "semantic_text": "ci/check-cherry-picks: improve error handling\n\nWe recently moved the $commits variable out of a \"subshell in a\nherestring\", let's do the same for the list of branches, where errors\nwould be silently swallowed as well.\n\nAlso reformat the expressions slightly, we have enough line-length.\n\n(cherry picked from commit e2a37921691a3c0131114795d4b756aa7bd5d4a4)", "semantic_meaning": null, "semantic_ref": null, "semantic_label": "benign", "semantic_content_type": "real", "timestamp": 1614441471.0}
